summary:
i am a photographer from the netherlands. in 1990 i started art triq - a studio for graphic design and communication. you can say i'm a creative thinker and i create strong images for commercial and publishing purposes. my work has a personal approach and i look for an appropriate and contemporary touch in my images. 

companies, publishers, creatives, models, artists, families, politicians, vamps, celebs and persons who are looking for a different style, please contact me for a briefing and recent price-rates. 

thank you for your interest in my profile.

specialties: photography, fashion, advertisement, product, branding and identity, websites, visional communication, graphic design and more ...
